title: Merge of your list on my data and update with latest projects
body:
Hi Onur!

I merged your updates into my datasets and used a custom generator to "repair" your list.
I fixed typos, missing links, missing descriptions and alphabetical order of sections. Then I added a dozen of new projects to the dataset. If you find any problems feel free to contact me and I will be glad to fix them :smile:

I also publish the refactored project on Github (https://github.com/zenkay/bigdata-ecosystem) with dataset and generators. I also add a link to your project into the README.

Have a nice weekend!
Andrea
